ğŸ”¹ 39. Design a fraud detection query

`sql
SELECT UserID, COUNT(*) AS Attempts
FROM Transactions
WHERE Amount > 10000 AND Timestamp BETWEEN DATEADD(MINUTE, -5, GETDATE()) AND GETDATE()
GROUP BY UserID
HAVING COUNT(*) > 3;
`

